						<p>@<b>Sockpuppet</b> Well let's see here.</p>
<blockquote><p>First you start with a very weak point saying that group sovereignity is either vested in one man or donâ€™t exist. Thatâ€™s true. </p></blockquote>
<p>If it's true why would you think it's weak ? Truth is never weak.</p>
